  <entry>
    <title>Ant-Design-Vue版本兼容问题</title>
    <url>/2023/02/05/Ant-Design-Vue%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leo-56/anki-pics/another/pics/202302051657929.png" alt="image-20230205133928955"></p>
<p>又一个教训，前端开发一定要注意版本号的匹配，高版本不一定兼容低版本，这种 UI 组件也不能掉以轻心</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p><strong>组件的版本要与文档的版本配套</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/leo-56/anki-pics/another/pics/202302051657801.png" alt="image-20230205134047973"></p>
<h3 id="踩坑经过"><a href="#踩坑经过" class="headerlink" title="踩坑经过"></a>踩坑经过</h3><p>今天在 Vue3 中引入 Ant Design Vue 后，跟着视频教程走，下一步就是布局</p>
<p>在官网复制以下 css </p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#components-layout-demo-top-side</span> <span class="selector-class">.logo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">float</span>: left;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">120px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">31px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">16px</span> <span class="number">24px</span> <span class="number">16px</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0.3</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.ant-row-rtl</span> <span class="selector-id">#components-layout-demo-top-side</span> <span class="selector-class">.logo</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">float</span>: right;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">16px</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">16px</span> <span class="number">24px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.site-layout-background</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="number">#fff</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>其中 <code>.log</code> 选择器始终处于灰色，IDEA 也提示该选择器处于没有生效的状态，自然，它所涉及的 css 也没有生效</p>
<p>后面才知道是 <strong>Ant Design Vue 版本</strong>的问题</p>
<p>我当时选择的是 <code>2.0.0-rc.3</code>，可是官网上的 <code>2.X</code> 版本的文档指定了是 <code>2.2.8</code>，当时是看到了，本来以为没什么，谁想到在第一步就出现了问题</p>
<p>后面换成了 <code>2.2.8</code> 之后，尽管还是处于灰色的状态，但是页面已经恢复正常了</p>
]]></content>
